Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:23.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}勇敢之光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:28.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}伸出手去你会见到光
