Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:14.01,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}至少纵声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.26,0:22:25.40,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}恸哭和绝望之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.98,0:22:31.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}等待我们的命运
