Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:41.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}为之奋斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:46.71,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}当下的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:53.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你哭泣的夜晚之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:59.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}藏有遥远未来的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:03.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}静谧在等待你
